    <h1 style="color:white; margin-bottom:16px;">How a PEO actually works</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);">No jargon. No sales pitch. Everything a business owner needs to understand before deciding whether a PEO is worth exploring.</p>
